    "William MacDonald": "Furnishings of the Temple (7:13-51) F. Dedication of the Temple (Chap. 8) G. Solomon `[char_Solomon_Ref]`'s Fame (Chaps. 9, 10)\n4. His Navy (9:26-28)\n4. Death of Jeroboam's Son (14:1-20) C. King Rehoboam of Judah (cont'd) (14:21-31) D. King Abijam of Judah (15:1-8) E. King Asa of Judah (15:9-24) F. King Nadab of Israel (15:25-27) G. King Baasha of Israel (15:28-16:7) H. King Elah of Israel (16:8-10) I. King Zimri of Israel (16:11-20) J. King Tibni of Israel (16:21, 22) K. King Omri of Israel (16:23-28) L. King Ahab of Israel and the Prophet Elijah (16:29-22:40)\n4. Elijah's Challenge to the Priests of Baal (18:1-19)",
